Description:
RefPower is an Italian company based in Lonigo (VI) which is dedicated to after-sales activities on semi-hermetic refrigeration compressors. RefPower services include:
- Analysis and diagnostics;
- Overhauls and repairs;
- Supply of spare parts;
- Mechanical machining and motor rewinding;
- Supply of replacement compressors (new or, if available, refurbished), eventually also for rental;
- Technical study for the replacement of screw compressors with models by Palladio Compressors, our subsidiary;
- Training courses on screw compressors.

RefPower operates on compressors of all brands, as #RefComp, #Bitzer, #Hanbell, #Daikin, #McQuay, #Carrier, #Frascold, #Sabroe, #York, #Mayekawa and many others.

RefPower is also co-owner of PALLADIO COMPRESSORS, a company dedicated to the production of high-efficiency screw compressors, which can also be used for substitution of equipment from other brands.

Since 2024 RefPower is official Danfoss service partner for BOCK (#RefCare service program) and Turbocor (#TASP – Turbocor Approved Service Provider) compressors.
RefPower has a dedicated division, named RefPower Marine, for service activities on vessels and offshore platforms.

Since 2016 RefPower is exclusive Italian distributor of #DunAn, the world leading manufacturer of refrigerant valves and heat exchangers.

Contact our experts: sales@refpower.eu
Discover more: www.refpower.eu

Seamark Group of Companies is an organization of several companies working in the reefer industry.

Seamark Reefer Solutions; 
Since 2002 one of the largest independent mobile Reefer Service Company in Europe. They carry out service on all major refrigerator & generators manufacturers in The Netherlands and Belgium. Together with customers and reefer manufacturers guidelines and their Engagement, Reliability, Flexibility and Quality, they offer a full Taylor made technical service for reefer and genset units. 
Seamark Reefer Solutions is since 2015 a certificated Carrier Caremax Service Center. CareMAX protocols cover all post-production stages of refrigerant handling, from procurement and testing, to storage and decanting, including maintenance of refrigerant-handling tools and how to train service technicians who handle refrigerants.

Seamark Monitoring Solutions; 
When a reefer container is loaded with temperature controlled cargo, and you want  to check, control and evaluate the required settings, Seamark Monitoring Solutions is you partner. They  can carry out this service on any location in the Rotterdam and Antwerp area. With this service you have the option to protect your cargo and avoid malfunctioning of the reefer container.

AM-Solution;
A dynamic and innovative company which brings more than 20 years of Maintenance and Repair knowledge into the industry. Experience from reefer- to electronic repairs and from spare parts to finished goods and logistics; they know how it works in every detail. With this knowledge, they create cost effective programs for large global, but also small local companies. AM-Solution does electronics repairs, develops innovative tools, consumable spare parts, consulting, advising, marketing and even implements sales programs into your market place. 
All our parts, repaired or produced, are made with the highest care and quality and are covered by one year full warranty.

Société spécialisée dans l'étude, l'installation et la maintenance des systèmes de climatisations et chauffage gaz. Créée en 1982, AGP est certifiée Qualibat depuis 2018. 

Notre priorité est de préserver les intérêts économiques de nos clients tout en assurant la meilleure solution technique. Chaque projet est unique et est étudié avec attention dans le respect du cahier des charges. Les matériels sont sélectionnés afin d’obtenir le meilleur rendement énergétique.

AGP offre les services suivants : 
- Étude et installation de matériel de climatisation, de réfrigération et de récupération d’énergie ; et chauffage gaz
- Étude thermique spécifique ; 
- Maintenance et dépannage de tout système thermique et climatique ;

