SDM Business Development, is a tailor-made consultancy, created with the purpose of leveraging customer business outcomes. Small by design, but flexible enough to fit your organizational needs, with practical and innovative solutions with the best cost benefit.

Built based on the experience of +30 years in the oil and gas sector, along with the most important companies in the oil and gas sectors worldwide, with a diverse experience across the value chain, onshore and offshore, up/middle/downstream projects.

Currently SDM represents Baltimore Aircoil Company (BAC) in Brazil. BAC offers the widest array of evaporative heat rejection and thermal storage equipment in the industry. Breadth of product enables BAC to provide its customers with optimized solutions to meet their specific needs. Whether an application calls for open or closed circuit, axial or centrifugal fan, special materials of construction or unique layout considerations, BAC has the right solution, now available in Brazil.

Portfolio of Experience:
•	Business Development;
•	Partnership, Regulatory Compliance;
•	Drilling Projects and Operations;
•	Offshore Decommission and Operations;
•	NORM Management (CNEN accredited);
•	LNG, CNG solutions;
•	Offshore Construction and Maintenance;
•	International Sourcing and Procurement;
•	Strategic Technologies e Products rollout;
•	Pipelines and processing facilities integrity;
•	Logistics partners;

